Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.38,0:00:12.53,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.22,0:00:15.28,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll change history.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.80,0:00:17.87,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to protect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.33,0:00:22.54,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I promise. I promise. I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.46,0:00:46.56,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,When is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.82,0:00:47.65,Default,SJ,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.65,0:00:50.28,Default,SJ,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking you what month and day it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.63,0:00:55.40,Default,SJ,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's December 21st...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.67,0:01:02.27,Default,SJ,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:25.17,Punchline-Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Punch Line
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.46,0:02:48.06,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,So anyway, I've really been through hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:50.98,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, one wrong move \Nand I could have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:52.87,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:54.23,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Did it go okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.49,0:02:58.11,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,The police investigation was rough, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:03:00.99,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,I just got back, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:03.90,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, we can talk about that later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.90,0:03:05.87,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Before that, here. Want one?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:13.46,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.62,0:03:21.55,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,What's his problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:25.55,Punchline-Ep_Title,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Panty Panic Returns
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:30.60,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.29,0:03:35.53,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:40.83,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.78,0:03:45.74,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Must be that thing they call PTSD.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:52.92,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! This isn't the time for celebrating!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:55.39,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Only ten days until New Year's Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.39,0:03:56.92,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.95,0:04:01.22,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, I'll try outlining \Neverything that's about to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:07.75,Punchline-Summary,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Cheermancy / Muhi discovered
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.56,0:04:07.31,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,23rd: Cheermancy; Muhi discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:13.55,Punchline-Summary,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Turtle Man = Tomoda attacks
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:11.63,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,24th: Turtle Man, a.k.a Tomoda, attacks;
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.59,0:04:13.55,Punchline-Summary2,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Miyazawa Kenji arrives
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:13.01,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Miya Ken arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.39,0:04:18.26,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I slept through this day, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.26,0:04:21.56,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I think they had a Christmas party or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:26.40,Punchline-Summary,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Meika discovered to be a robot
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.91,0:04:26.41,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,26th: Meika discovered to be a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.55,0:04:31.65,Punchline-Summary,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Gliese visits / Miyazawa Kenji attacks
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:31.13,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,27th: Gliese visits; Miya Ken attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.27,0:04:38.87,Punchline-Summary,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Ito in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.78,0:04:38.36,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,29th: Ito in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:42.62,Punchline-Summary,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Turtle Man = Tomoda Battle
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.48,0:04:42.63,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,30th: Battle with Turtle Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.78,0:04:49.13,Punchline-Summary2,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Meikaemon Party\NAsteroid Hits
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:48.25,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,31st: Meikaemon Party; asteroid hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:52.66,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,The two important dates \Nare the 24th and the 27th.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:55.31,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Tomoda attacks on the 24th,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:54.96,Punchline-SummaryRed,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,626)}Turtle Man = Tomoda attacks
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:58.78,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,and Gliese comes to Korai House on the 27th.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:59.50,Punchline-SummaryRed,,0000,0000,0000,,Gliese visits / Miyazawa Kenji attacks
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.91,0:05:01.94,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Those two must know something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.92,0:05:05.36,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Sitting around thinking won't help!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:06.76,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotta move!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.75,0:05:09.41,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to find them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.17,0:05:16.51,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.51,0:05:17.75,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Chiranosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:18.83,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.89,0:05:22.15,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I can still see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.15,0:05:25.09,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,You're still at the same spirit power level.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:27.73,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same as if you'd \Ntrained to become a psychic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.73,0:05:29.93,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,And? What was that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:32.39,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Chiranosuke's Code, number one:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.71,0:05:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must not change history \Nwithout my permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.28,0:05:37.14,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Number two:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.71,0:05:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must not tell anyone else the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.54,0:05:41.57,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:44.53,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Because then the plan will fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:47.24,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the previous Miya Ken.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:49.74,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,The previous Miya Ken?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:51.83,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,You saw him on the rooftop.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:54.50,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,That's you from the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:06:00.25,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I can't have you \Nbecoming {\i1}that{\i0} Miya Ken.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:02.02,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:04.75,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make it easy to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:09.18,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,First, this is the world you're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:13.40,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,And this train travels down \Nthe rail, toward the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:16.46,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,If it goes straight, it will arrive here,\Nat the worst-case scenario,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.46,0:06:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the New Year's Eve when the asteroid hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:21.40,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,That Miya Ken ended up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.91,0:06:23.56,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,But I need you to go
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.56,0:06:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,toward the New Year's Eve \Nwhere the asteroid doesn't strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.39,0:06:32.84,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond that is a supremely \Nhappy and peaceful future.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.23,0:06:35.80,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,To guide the world to that future is
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.80,0:06:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the ultimate purpose of the \NHuman Preservation Project.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:42.84,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,The Human Preservation Project?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:45.29,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,To stop the asteroid from falling,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.29,0:06:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,thereby protecting the human \Nspecies from extinction.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.06,0:06:55.60,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, you absolutely, unfailingly, \Nmust succeed in this project.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:58.32,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,That is your destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.97,0:07:00.39,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,My destiny?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:02.73,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,That's the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:06.91,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,That's why when your spirit \Nsees panties, humanity ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.21,0:07:07.78,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.09,0:07:12.86,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,A spirit without its body is \Nlike an egg without its shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.86,0:07:14.67,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicate and easily damaged,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:17.48,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,and sensitive to all kinds of stimuli.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:21.42,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,And what happens when such a spirit \Nbecomes excited twice in a row?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:28.86,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,You become infused with a massive \Ntorrent of excited energy, and your body
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.90,0:07:32.82,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,You undergo a technobreak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.31,0:07:34.43,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:38.39,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,That's the relationship between \Npanties and human extinction.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:41.52,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,By being exposed repeatedly to panties,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the person executing the operation is lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:46.76,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,And ultimately, the asteroid hits Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.35,0:07:48.98,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,How do I make sure I don't fail?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.24,0:07:51.14,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You wanna know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:55.58,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,There, I put all of them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.58,0:07:57.45,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:08:00.45,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Um, is that really all I have to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.01,0:08:03.31,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,If I just do the same thing as last time,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.31,0:08:04.79,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,won't history stay the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.03,0:08:06.43,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.43,0:08:08.08,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Just have faith in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.43,0:08:13.61,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.61,0:08:17.78,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Now Niconico Live Encoder \Nshould start automatically.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:18.78,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Next...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.78,0:08:19.62,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:22.10,Punchline-Secret_Box,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(375,1)}Akina's Secret Box
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:22.10,Punchline-Secret_Box2,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(375,1)}Don't look\Ninside!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:22.10,Punchline-Secret_Box_Danger,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(375,1)}Danger
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.71,0:08:22.10,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:27.61,Punchline-Nandala_Gandala,Text,0000,0000,0000,,The Indian Sacred Book\NNandala Gandala
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.43,0:08:26.08,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,My crazy sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:27.61,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd she give it this title?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.26,0:08:35.52,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.52,0:08:38.87,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't forget the word that \Nwas written in it, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:40.17,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:41.79,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,"U-turn," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.79,0:08:42.71,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:43.66,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.14,0:08:45.52,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to write it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:46.63,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.76,0:08:50.38,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I'd be admitting defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:54.33,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I used this when I failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.81,0:08:57.35,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,But this me won't fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.90,0:09:00.76,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,So I don't need to write it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.08,0:09:07.40,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening-ning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.71,0:09:09.65,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening-ning...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:11.65,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Yuta-kun, what happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:14.15,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Your room's plastered with talismans!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:17.92,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is, um... interior design.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:19.41,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.68,0:09:21.91,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,So what brings you here, Narugino?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.09,0:09:26.00,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, there are some kanji in \Nthis script that I couldn't read.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.02,0:09:27.92,Punchline-Encounter,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Encounter
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.77,0:09:29.67,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,"Encounter," I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:34.75,Punchline-Encounter,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Encounter
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.16,0:09:32.09,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,To meet unexpectedly,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:34.76,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,or make contact by accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:37.76,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you know a lot, Yuta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.15,0:09:40.54,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,But why come to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.54,0:09:42.90,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, you're so dense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:45.80,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Mikatan came to check up on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:47.30,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.71,0:09:47.30,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.95,0:09:48.65,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.10,0:09:53.29,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,She knows about what happened on \Nthe bus and at the river. Everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.57,0:09:54.90,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she's—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:56.40,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.93,0:09:59.41,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,But I haven't said anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:04.13,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.13,0:10:07.92,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I mean, thanks for teaching me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.64,0:10:10.07,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.86,0:10:12.25,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.21,0:10:18.30,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.54,0:10:21.14,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,'Sup!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.71,0:10:22.97,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:24.75,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:28.29,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,I thought maybe you were tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.29,0:10:29.14,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:33.15,Punchline-Genki_Maker,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Genki Maker\N{\c&H1187AC&}Z
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:33.15,Punchline-Daihatsu,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Daihatsu Pharmaceuticals
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.76,0:10:31.24,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.24,0:10:33.15,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,My special drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.44,0:10:37.65,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,For nutritional fortification and \Nreplenishment when you're exhausted!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:40.41,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Genki Maker!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:43.03,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,It seems poisonous, no matter how I look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:45.50,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Fight poison with poison!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.50,0:10:47.57,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,So it {\i1}is{\i0} poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:52.33,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, isn't that Narugino's \Nscript you're holding?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:54.74,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she forgot it here just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:56.76,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring it back to her later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.44,0:10:58.49,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:10.10,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.81,0:11:15.52,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,So that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.95,0:11:19.68,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, um... what happens next, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.16,0:11:21.86,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I think my spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.89,0:11:29.32,Punchline-Flashback,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,What happens when such a spirit \Nbecomes excited twice in a row?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.84,0:11:33.36,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! I have to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:45.23,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Ito.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:47.13,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.38,0:11:54.56,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this room's always so messy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:57.90,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess I'll take a shower for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.58,0:12:04.16,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, I have to grab some more shampoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.76,0:12:09.29,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,No! If Ito comes out now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.11,0:12:14.88,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:15.84,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:36.79,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.57,0:12:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wai—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.12,0:12:41.36,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry, Ito! I didn't mean to!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.36,0:12:44.86,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,You animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.86,0:12:54.29,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Where did that book go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:54.92,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:56.41,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,You pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.41,0:12:57.58,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:12:58.92,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Creep!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.07,0:13:00.77,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Stop... Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.11,0:13:01.59,Punchline-Harakiri_Harrassment,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Hara{\c&H7D7B79&}kiri Harassment
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.11,0:13:01.59,Punchline-Harakiri_Harrassment,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\a3\fs20\c&H5F594A&}Harahara Production Group
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.66,0:13:03.54,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.07,0:13:09.35,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's on the top shelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:14.77,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,No you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.89,0:13:22.37,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Salt, huh? Sorry, I'm out right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.37,0:13:24.65,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll borrow some from Mikatan, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:26.96,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, if you're going to see Narugino...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.96,0:13:29.12,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Could you return this to her for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:31.41,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, but what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:32.78,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,A script.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:33.91,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,For She's Mei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.31,0:13:49.39,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,No... This isn't, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:53.31,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:58.42,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,You! Give me back my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:03.69,Punchline-Punch_Perms_Book,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Punch Perms and\NChirashi Sushi
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.81,0:14:09.57,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.55,0:14:09.57,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Rabura!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:14.54,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:22.04,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I changed history a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.95,0:14:24.63,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.58,0:14:28.93,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:30.41,Punchline-Harakiri_Harrassment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs22}Hara{\c&H7A7A7A&}kiri Harassment
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:30.41,Punchline-Harakiri_Harrassment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10\fs18\c&H525249&}Harahara Production Group
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.74,0:14:38.51,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.51,0:14:40.23,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the book!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.49,0:14:43.52,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, did they get mixed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:46.74,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,It must have happened when I crashed into him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:59.00,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.76,0:15:11.45,Punchline-Punch_Perms_Book2,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1168)}She's Mei Musical Project \NDebut Piece\N{\fs24}Punch Perms and Chirashi Sushi
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.50,0:15:11.73,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,The apples of Tsugaru Mountain...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:17.81,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,This sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:20.81,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I've walked all this way, and made no progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:23.49,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't get into the
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.49,0:15:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Qmay Group headquarters with all \Nthe police and reporters there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:28.82,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,And I couldn't find Tomoda, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.73,0:15:30.84,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,That leaves...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.65,0:15:32.46,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Rabura?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.87,0:15:33.62,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Rabura!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:35.17,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.63,0:15:40.41,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Were you out for {\i1}yuuhan{\i0} (dinner)?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:43.12,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,What? It's only 4:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:45.79,Punchline-Koraikan,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Korai \NHouse
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.12,0:15:45.23,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean a {\i1}yuurei hanto{\i0} (ghost hunt).
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:47.27,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.27,0:15:50.30,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anyway, listen, there's \Nsomething I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.67,0:15:52.80,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Can you tell me how to get \Nin contact with Gliese?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:54.69,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.69,0:15:56.47,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know about Gliese-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:58.23,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.67,0:16:02.84,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.36,0:16:14.49,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Tomoda!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:18.70,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.01,0:16:23.04,Default,Tomoda,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:26.09,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up and get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:30.00,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:38.26,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:43.27,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, you're not allowed to \Nchange history without my permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.21,0:16:47.05,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.95,0:16:49.75,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,The cooperation of the tenants
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.75,0:16:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is vital to the success of the \NHuman Preservation Project.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.19,0:16:57.49,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Try to remember all those things that \Nhappened in the previous history.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.10,0:17:00.23,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,There was Cheermancy, \Nand the thing with Muhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.23,0:17:02.76,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Mikatan and Meika's identities were exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:05.02,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone got into fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.78,0:17:10.34,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Each of those events brought \Nyou all closer together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:14.16,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,That's important to this operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.85,0:17:17.38,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,So in order to create those bonds,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.38,0:17:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we need to recreate history up to a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.76,0:17:23.27,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,And if we don't protect it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.51,0:17:26.23,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,So far, six billion, three hundred \Nseventy-three million,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,one hundred fifty-three thousand, \Nseven hundred forty yous
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.29,0:17:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have broken that code, and went on to fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.60,0:17:35.52,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to be the six billion, \Nthree hundred seventy-three million,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.52,0:17:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,one hundred fifty-three thousand, \Nseven hundred forty-first,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.31,0:17:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.76,0:17:42.54,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll tell you this:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.05,0:17:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is no "next" for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.24,0:17:46.54,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:50.05,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,If you fail this operation, it's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.05,0:17:51.55,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Not for me, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.60,0:17:54.92,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,I have the next possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.16,0:17:57.47,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,The next possibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.82,0:18:00.15,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about the next you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.41,0:18:03.35,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this might be a dumb question, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:08.94,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I end up out-of-body?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:11.90,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You can't even figure that out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.25,0:18:17.38,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,It's because your spirit came from \Nthe future and possessed your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.38,0:18:22.09,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,So then, my original spirit \Ngot kicked out of my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.86,0:18:23.67,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.67,0:18:25.79,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,What about when I possessed Rabura, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.79,0:18:30.20,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,No, Rabura's spirit remained\Nattached to her body then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.20,0:18:31.47,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:33.46,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it just me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:37.22,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,You were Yubafied when you'd \Npassed out at the river side.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:39.51,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,While you're Yubafied,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your subliminal mind can \Neject the conscious mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.22,0:18:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,creating a state in which your \Nspirit can easily detach.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:50.94,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Try to remember what happened \Nduring the summer nine years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.08,0:19:01.95,Punchline-Flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about everything that's happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.63,0:19:06.37,Punchline-Flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm guilty of being an accomplice in the project.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:09.53,Punchline-Flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing this to atone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.53,0:19:11.27,Punchline-Flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,I want to end things right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.67,0:19:51.08,Punchline-Flashback,Akina,0000,0000,0000,,You're finally awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.64,0:19:54.00,Punchline-Flashback,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:55.84,Punchline-Flashback,Akina,0000,0000,0000,,You're at my grandpa's and my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.19,0:20:00.07,Punchline-Flashback,Akina,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa found you this morning \Nand brought you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.07,0:20:02.09,Punchline-Flashback,Akina,0000,0000,0000,,You were passed out by the river, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.65,0:20:06.22,Punchline-Flashback,Akina,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't introduced myself yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:07.60,Punchline-Flashback,Akina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Akina.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:09.46,Punchline-Flashback,Akina,0000,0000,0000,,Iridatsu Akina.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.46,0:20:10.57,Punchline-Flashback,Akina,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.07,0:20:13.35,Punchline-Flashback,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.99,0:20:19.21,Punchline-Flashback,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.09,0:20:22.20,Punchline-Flashback,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Chiyoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.04,0:20:27.05,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:32.35,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Right before you three fell into \Nthe dam, you were Yubafied.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.82,0:20:39.58,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Just then, you were struck by lightning, \Nand the three of you swapped spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.72,0:20:43.51,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Guriko's spirit entered your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.94,0:20:46.76,Default,Chiranosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Chiyoko's spirit entered Guriko's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.24,0:20:50.46,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,And I went into Chiyoko's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.21,0:20:55.05,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.42,0:21:01.39,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:04.03,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't here during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.39,0:21:06.44,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,I held on to a delivery for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.44,0:21:08.03,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.86,0:21:19.02,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,From my sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.02,0:21:20.55,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I have a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.55,0:21:24.05,Punchline-Shes_Mei,Text,0000,0000,0000,,She's Mei
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.48,0:21:26.55,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Dude, seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.65,0:21:29.51,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
